Instead of a basic HTML website, I recommend building SharusuriEdTech using a modern, industry-standard stack:

HTML5
CSS3 (organized with reusable components)
JavaScript (ES6 modules)
Bootstrap 5 or Tailwind CSS
Font Awesome icons
AOS (animations)
Swiper.js (sliders)
FullCalendar (calendar)
Chart.js (dashboard)
PHP or Node.js backend (if needed)
MySQL database
GitHub Actions for deployment

This structure is scalable and suitable for a professional educational platform.

